{"tid":1505402,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"經過今晚荃灣遊行 係時候轉抗爭方向","createTime":"2019-08-25T14:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T03:01:37.000Z","uid":284817,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5950ba64f1e9e58bb7172ee536c6831ad5753912","tid":1505402,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:04:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">經過咁多場遊行，政府都係唔理我哋訴求，但一佔機場就翌日出嚟見人。<br />\n<br />\n睇咗好多post，覺得係時候轉手法，專打政府死穴：就係機場！<br />\n<br />\n機場！<br />\n<br />\n機場！<br />\n<br />\n機場！<br />\n<br />\n同埋真心，睇過之前一個post，覺得一至五夜晚七點搞快閃扮遊行拖垮黨鐵係有得諗，因為有一班放工嘅人加入埋，但黨鐵又捉唔出邊個係抗爭嘅，而且禁制令仍然生效，咁嘅鐵路抗爭模式先係最保險。就睇佢封得邊個站。最好我哋㨂喺轉車站扮遊行，假如封金鐘、中環、太子就gg了。<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇人諗可唔可以JR（司法覆核）/禁制黨鐵嘅決定？</span>"},{"pid":"3ac494bcc4dcc8b06d94caac4a2d8e0f099dc880","tid":1505402,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e9a7088ccc55ae7a02c18ef1af7f9984f0d3b80","tid":1505402,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:33:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e9ff62a1dcb0dc950aeafd1c1c166c224dc04f6","tid":1505402,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0267120f71434e29bbd2d8d785acee2922312d6","tid":1505402,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a3d9a025335e38e9fc1acac19108494032adaeb","tid":1505402,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa662825db1513959e912be38e8459481b9000ec","tid":1505402,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61714ec922cf25a59c085621a06a4a551f8d5254","tid":1505402,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a864dd69b2b9c4734e9d61f07f85470117e3175","tid":1505402,"uid":28